title: Proactiv Solution Deep Cleansing Wash, 8 Oz
description:
Your face isn't the only place that can suffer from acne. That's why we created Proactiv Solution Deep Cleansing Wash, a gentle all-over cleanser perfect for face and body.
Benefits: 
Perfect for occasional use when you want an extra deep clean

Finely milled exfoliating beads smooth away dead skin cells

Soothing botanicals calm skin as it exfoliates

Special formula containing 2% salicylic acid helps unclog pores and reduce oiliness to help prevent future breakouts

title: Bare Escentuals Maximum Coverage Concealer Brush
description: Broken capillaries. Scars. Blemishes. Conceal and conquer any imperfection with this soft brush, which gives you fuller, more concentrated coverage. That's because the firm, medium-sized brush head holds more SPF 20 Multi-Tasking Concealer. Use a patting technique to cover imperfections before or after applying your foundation, and you'll get maximum coverage that blends completely and doesn't leave a line.
